title: Sidewall
description: A spray of roses with Rococo scrolls behind it is arranged in diagonal rows. Background is printed in wide vertical bands alternating with plain and satin finish field. Top left side of each band has a leaf border. Entire paper is embossed with fine horizontal lines. Printed in selvedge: "Waterfast, 5375 Run 8, Birge, Made in U.S.A."
name: Sidewall
